Name: Just Another Runner
About the game: Take a quick enigmatic run up memory lane. Don't even think about slowing down, 'cause the present surely won't. Run, jump, slide and boost through four levels of this short, satirical and mildly abstract exploration of contemporary nostalgia. Maintain your boost to keep running and break your 'Boost Record'. Featuring FMV cutscenes. Come on up and stay a while.
